# Admin Monetization Console Rule

Monetization admin is a revenue operations console, not a simple plan list.

Required:
- tabs: Overview, Plans, Entitlements, Quotas, Subscriptions, Trials & Coupons, Ads, Analytics, Audit
- KPI cards
- plan management
- entitlement assignment
- quota policy and quota override management
- subscription lifecycle visibility
- coupon/trial configuration
- ad placement management
- monetization analytics
- audit log
- RBAC-aware actions
- confirmation + audit reason for sensitive mutations

Forbidden:
- hard-coded premium/free checks
- fake revenue numbers
- single generic status chart as the whole page
- mutation without permission check
- mutation without audit log
- exposing provider secrets
- ads inside active learning sessions